        . apply ih Γ (by intro x hx; specialize hΓ x hx; simp [hδ, hx] at hΓ; assumption) h_conj;
    exact h_no_xi (encode φ) (insert φ Γ) (by simp [hΓ]; apply monotone_construction (by simp); simp [construction]; exact h) (by simpa);
